No. 11-5707. Jeffrey Sanders, Petitioner v. United States District Court for the Eastern District of Michigan. 565 U.S. 938, 132 S. Ct. 447,

181 L. Ed. 2d 251,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7230. October 11, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 653 F. Supp. 2d 715.
